form.congress: One Hundred Thirteenth Congress of the United States of America
form.enrolled-dateline: Begun and held at the City of Washington on Thursday, the third day of January, two thousand and thirteen
form.official-title: To designate the United States courthouse and Federal building located at 118 South Mill Street, in Fergus Falls, Minnesota, as the Edward J. Devitt United States Courthouse and Federal Building.

section.text: The United States courthouse and Federal building located at 118 South Mill Street, in Fergus Falls, Minnesota, shall be known and designated as the Edward J. Devitt United States Courthouse and Federal Building.

Any reference in a law, map, regulation, document, paper, or other record of the United States to the United States courthouse and Federal building referred to in section 1 shall be deemed to be a reference to the Edward J. Devitt United States Courthouse and Federal Building.

attestation-group.role: Speaker of the House of Representatives.
Vice President of the United States and President of the Senate.
